title: Pak Police Seizes Ammunition, Video Goes Viral as J&K Incident
subtitle: Fact Check Pakistan Video: A video of police officials recovering ammunition from a motorcycle’s seat has been circulating on social media claiming it to be from the erstwhile state of Jammu and Kashmir.
author: www.thequint.com
vclaim:
A video of police officials recovering ammunition from a motorcycle's seat has been circulating on social media with a claim that it is from the erstwhile state of Jammu and Kashmir.

It loosely translates to “People say police in Jammu & Kashmir stop vehicles intentionally. Now what will people say about this.”

Several social media users shared the video on Facebook and Twitter with the same claim.
